text: 26.65 Mat 9.3, Mak 14.63, Jon 10.33, Apo 14.14 26.65-66 Wkp 24.16 Jisas anɨb agek, bɨ God nop sɨbogep bɨawl yɨbɨl ak, taynen anɨb agup agɨl, chech ne okok ke tɨg talɨkɨlɨg agak, Ne God nop agjulɨg agosup agak. Taynen binɨb ogɨnap sek agnɨgɨnɨgun agak. God nop agjuwep takaw ak mɨseŋ agup nɨbi nepɨm agak.
